          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire-flame-curved"></i></div>
            <h4>Reduces Inflammation</h4>
            <p>HA injections have anti-inflammatory properties that reduce swelling, warmth, and stiffness around the joint.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
